eme to entice potential investors in the United States to =0Ainvest funds w=
ith the defendants. The defendants allegedly lured investors to =0Athe webs=
ites by placing fictitious comments from purported clients on social =0Amed=
ia and in investment group chats praising the representatives=E2=80=99 trad=
