hese complex structures, called double- or second-layer SPVs, create opport=
unities for misrepresentation and even fraud.</p> <p style=3D"margin: 16px =
0;">They also charge for access. Investors in these second-rung SPVs often =
pay more in fees than those investing in the first layer or directly in the=
